trans-unit.source: Provides access to the state of the control designer in the design host through the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentDesignerStateService" /> interface.
trans-unit.target: Fornece acesso ao estado do designer de controle no host de design por meio da interface <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentDesignerStateService" />.
Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesignerState> class is a wrapper for the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentDesignerStateService> interface, which is the interface between a designer and a design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesignerState> classe é um wrapper para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentDesignerStateService> interface, que é a interface entre um designer e um host de design, como [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/includes/vsprvslong-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The name of the item to set or retrieve from the state collection.
trans-unit.target: O nome do item a ser definido ou recuperado da coleção de estado.

trans-unit.source: Represents one element, identified by the given key, in the state collection for a control designer.
trans-unit.target: Representa um elemento, identificado pela chave fornecida, na coleção de estado de um designer de controle.
